            "text": "<p>For bespoke commissions, high-value remodelling projects, and significant valuations, our initial home consultation within our specified service areas is complimentary. </p><p>We view this as an essential part of the luxury Griffin & Co experience. If you are enquiring solely for a minor repair collection, a small travel or secure postage fee may apply, which we will clearly discuss with you beforehand.</p>",
