            "text": "<p>One of our expert jewellers or master goldsmiths will travel to your home at a scheduled time that suits you. </p><p>For design consultations, we bring extensive portfolios, various precious metal samples, and a curated selection of loose diamonds or gemstones for you to view in your own lighting. </p><p>We also bring professional sizing tools to ensure absolute precision.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
