          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Is my jewellery safe if you collect it for repair?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Completely. We offer secure, fully insured collection from your home directly to our Chichester workshop. </p><p>Crucially, all repair and remodelling work is conducted safely on-site by our in-house master goldsmiths. Your precious family heirlooms never leave our hands or get sent to third-party factories.</p>",
